\c 57
\s Rugare rwomwoyo pakati penjodzi
\d Kumutungamiriri wokuimba; nomuimbirwo weAritasheti. Pisarema raDhavhidhi, rwiyo rweMikitami; panguva yaa‑
\s katiza Sauro pabako.
\p
\v 57
\v 1 . Ndinzwirei tsitsi, Mwari, ndinzwirei tsitsi;
\s Nokuti mweya wangu unotizira kwamuri;
\s Zvirokwazvo, ndichatizira kumumvuri wamapapiro enyu, Kusvikira njodzi dzapfuura.
\p
\v 2 Ndichadanidzira kuna Mwari Wokumusorosoro;
\s Kuna Mwari anondiitira zvose.
\p
\v 3 Achatuma mubatsiri ari kudenga, andiponese,
\s Kana iye, anovavarira kundimedza, achindishora;
\s Mwari achatuma tsitsi dzake nezvokwadi yake.
\p
\v 4 Mweya wangu uri pakati peshumba; Ndinovata pasi pakati pavanopfuta somoto,
\s Ivo vanakomana vavanhu, vana meno
\s anenge mapfumo nemiseve, Uye rurimi rwavo munondo unopinza.
\p
\v 5 hni mulcuckwe Mwari, pamusoto
\s pokudenga-denga;
\s Kurumbidzwa kwenyu ngakuve kumusoro kwapasi pose.
\p
\v 6 Vakateyira tsoka dzangu mumbure; Mweya wangu wakakotamiswa;
\s Vakachera hunza pamberi pangu; Vawira mukati mayo vamene.
\p
\v 7 Mwoyo wangu wakasimba, Mwari, mwoyo wangu wakasimba; Ndichaimba, zvirokwazvo,
\s ndichaimba
\s nziyo dzokurumbidza.
\p
\v 8 Muka iwe mwoyo wangu, muka iwe
\s mutengeranwa nembira; Ini ndimene ndichamuka mangwanani.
\p
\v 9 Ndichakuvongai, Ishe, pakati pendudzi dzavanhu;
\s Ndichakuimbirai nziyo dzokurumbidza pakati pavahedheni.
\p
\v 1 ° Nokuti ngoni dzenyu ihuru kusvikira kudenga-denga,
\s Zvokwadi yenyu inosvikira kudenga rose.
\p
\v 11 Imi mukudzwe Mwari, kumusoro kwokudenga-denga;
\s Kurumbidzwa kwenyu ngakuve kumusoro kwapasi pose.
